# Mode: Recommended Professional Go AllowListing Template

# 1. Ignore absolutely everything by default to prevent smartphone junk logs
*

# 2. Hard-Allowlist essential project files and configuration source codes
!/.gitignore
!*.go
!*.js
!go.sum
!go.mod
!package.json
!package-lock.json
!README.md
!LICENSE

# 3. Allowlist institutional multi-chain directory structures
!/blockchain-core/
!/api-gateway/
!/mobile-app/
!/assets/

# 4. Recursively allow subdirectories tracking for core scripts
!*/

# 5. Explicitly block sensitive development environment variables
.env
.env.*
node_modules/
*.exe
*.test
